?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapp3.legco.gov.hk%2Fors%2Fchinese%2FInvite.aspx%3FInvId%3D10000267&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfgDpGYGFnKQRHckm7FIFNPY%3D&h=744e360c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://app3.legco.gov.hk/ors/chinese/Invite.aspx?InvId=10000267</a><br />\n<br />\n星期六得閒就報名去，唔得閒就交意見書<br />\n有冇巴絲得閒幫手寫template<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 返緊工寫唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nP牌推唔到大家幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:57:09.000Z","msg":"本人反對禁止蒙面法。原因如下：<br />\n<br />\n第一，此法違反《基本法》27條：「香港居民享有言論、新聞、出版的自由，結社、集會、遊行、示威的自由，組織和參加工會、罷工的權利和自由」。政府將《禁蒙面法》適用於合法遊行集會，令人質疑此舉的真正目的是阻嚇一般市民和學生不要上街抗議，否則承擔被秋後算帳的後果。𣎴少市民害怕在集會露面會影響其工作或私隱，例如公司的政治立場與員工不符，員工擔心參加合法集會會被公司䜔責；同志遊行的參與者希望爭取平權，但礙於社會歧視和壓力，暫時未能露面表態等。因此，此法嚴重損害市民無畏無懼地行使言論自由的權利。<br />\n<br />\n第二，此法對警員及香港市民雙重標準。<br />\n《禁蒙面法》生效後，一方面是警員依然遮蓋其委任證，甚至戴黑口罩雙重隱瞞身份。另一方面，普通市民連戴衛生口罩出外也隨時被警員截停查問。例如，不少記者被警員扯下其防催淚彈的面罩。（註一）有患癌症的市民展示其醫生紙卻被警員視為偽造文件等。（註二）法例通過後的穩定社會成效未見，但市民對政府和警方的不滿卻再創新高！<br />\n<br />\n因此，禁蒙面法只會增加民憤，完全無法做到預期的止暴制亂的效果。希望政府能順應民意，取消惡法。 <br />\n<br />\n第三，香港空氣污染指數愈來愈嚴重，全因警察胡亂放催淚彈，促使有需要使用衛生口罩！保護其個人身體健康 <br />\n<br />\n香港市民  XXX上<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n註一：-記者遭警強扯面罩<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/391108/禁蒙面法-記者遭警強扯面罩-黃定光-記者無特權違反警方指示\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F391108%2F%E7%A6%81%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E6%B3%95-%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E9%81%AD%E8%AD%A6%E5%BC%B7%E6%89%AF%E9%9D%A2%E7%BD%A9-%E9%BB%83%E5%AE%9A%E5%85%89-%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E7%84%A1%E7%89%B9%E6%AC%8A%E9%81%95%E5%8F%8D%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%8C%87%E7%A4%BA&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfgDpGYGFnKQRHckm7FIFNPY%3D&h=18ee19ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/391108/禁蒙面法-記者遭警強扯面罩-黃定光-記者無特權違反警方指示</a><br />\n<br />\n註二：癌漢戴口罩 警屈偽造醫生紙<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191104/GHUMTYKXLOJXF6YRET3ZKZN4RI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191104%2FGHUMTYKXLOJXF6YRET3ZKZN4RI%2F&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfgDpGYGFnKQRHckm7FIFNPY%3D&h=a58aa410\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191104%2FGHUMTYKXLOJXF6YRET3ZKZN4RI%2F&h=1c50dcfa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191104/GHUMTYKXLOJXF6YRET3ZKZN4RI/</a>"},{"pid":"178636e582f8b6225f173f8fe1822bebbb0e9f90","tid":1692778,"uid":332571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:45:52.000Z","msg":"幫手推！"},{"pid":"fa6e148b416cf04b2c01f12ede5f8090f995721c","tid":1692778,"uid":332571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:46:04.000Z","msg":"推推推！"},{"pid":"1060df1ca45371de779fa82ef007636f4c1016b4","tid":1692778,"uid":332571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:46:35.000Z","msg":"我已經send咗！"},{"pid":"2310c72cf37ab9f44c5a9817467655e87c2a96af","tid":1692778,"uid":332571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:47:01.000Z","msg":"今次超級鬼祟 無咩人知道"},{"pid":"9c3385c12ac51686d5e5b2e7261fd51bdab68365","tid":1692778,"uid":332571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:47:14.000Z","msg":"繼續幫手推"},{"pid":"b734d2668878ada149d3ac7f642393e8008ff47f","tid":1692778,"uid":332571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:47:37.000Z","msg":"5點前呀！！！！"},{"pid":"7dc9e3b8f2723ada1ab783d1052b518fb5669f40","tid":1692778,"uid":332571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:54:38.000Z","msg":"繼續推推"},{"pid":"ee1c42635a362895a8a2ac01737d971756c89ec0","tid":1692778,"uid":154892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T07:34:19.000Z","msg":"推"}]}